    html_content: "<p>Into the Woods Festival is a magic little event deep in the Swedish forest.</p>",
    quote: "Into the Woods is an off-grid festival deep inside the Swedish forest. The landscape is natural with a beautiful little lake as the backdrop for the stage. We strive to make the festival as sustainable as possible. 'Bottled up sunshine' harvested during the day, stored in batteries, gives us the possibility to keep the party running until late night.\n\nGenre-wise we try to mix the lineup as much as possible, jazz, electronic, folk/world, reggae, americana... Beyond the music, participants at the festival can join a vast variety of workshops, lectures, activities and adventures. Amongst many things, the floating sauna is very popular.",
